        <div class="card mx-auto mb-5">
          <div class="card-body offset-2" id="welcome">
            <h2 class="card-title">About Us</h2>
            <p>Full Spectrum is a forum for families of children with Autism Spectrum Disorder. Our hope is to create a
              community where
              families can gather
              to share ideas, discuss issues, as well as access resources and events in the community. While this is a
              free website for families, a user
              account must be created to access resources, write blog posts, and share in discussions with other users.
              To create your account, please click on the button below.
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
              <!-- Button trigger modal -->
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#ModalLong">
                Sign Up
              </button>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
